717705f-a.title: Manhattan: Broadway - 106th Street
717705f-a.text:
Broadway, east side, north from 106th Street. The Olympia
Theatre, on the S.W. corner of 107th Street, is shown in the centre.
The clearing in the foreground will be occupied by a new fifteen-
story apartment house.
October 13, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
